sources.title: Climate Change Makes Birds Erase Humans | Worst Movie Ever Made | Birdemic 3: Sea Eagle
sources.description:
From writer/director James Nguyen comes this new sequel to his BIRDEMIC: SHOCK AND TERROR, "the worst film ever made and a true cult hit" (The Guardian): When global warming triggers chaos along the Northern California coast, two scientific researchers will discover tender romance, appalling CGI, automatic weapons, and attacks by sea eagles that could lead to the extinction of life on earth. 
2022.  Stars: Ryan Lord, Julia Culbert, Marc DeNola
